{
  "video_id": "8Y9ppbU0864",
  "title": "David Hoffman: Catch Sputnik mania!",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 21330.0,
      "end_time": 24330.0,
      "text": "Fifty years ago in the old Soviet Union,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 24330.0,
      "end_time": 27330.0,
      "text": "a team of engineers was secretly moving a large object"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 27330.0,
      "end_time": 30330.0,
      "text": "through a desolate countryside."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 30330.0,
      "end_time": 33330.0,
      "text": "With it, they were hoping to capture the minds of people everywhere"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 33330.0,
      "end_time": 36330.0,
      "text": "by being the first to conquer outer space."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 36330.0,
      "end_time": 38330.0,
      "text": "The rocket was huge."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 38330.0,
      "end_time": 40330.0,
      "text": "And packed in its nose was a silver ball"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 40330.0,
      "end_time": 43330.0,
      "text": "with two radios inside."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 44330.0,
      "end_time": 47330.0,
      "text": "On October 4, 1957, they launched their rocket."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 47330.0,
      "end_time": 50330.0,
      "text": "One of the Russian scientists wrote at the time:"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 50330.0,
      "end_time": 52330.0,
      "text": "\"We are about to create a new planet"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 52330.0,
      "end_time": 55330.0,
      "text": "that we will call Sputnik."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 55330.0,
      "end_time": 57330.0,
      "text": "In the olden days, explorers"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 57330.0,
      "end_time": 60330.0,
      "text": "like Vasco da Gama and Columbus"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 60330.0,
      "end_time": 63330.0,
      "text": "had the good fortune to open up the terrestrial globe."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 64330.0,
      "end_time": 67330.0,
      "text": "Now we have the good fortune to open up space."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 67330.0,
      "end_time": 71330.0,
      "text": "And it is for those in the future to envy us our joy.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 72330.0,
      "end_time": 75330.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re watching snippets from \"Sputnik,\" my fifth documentary feature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 76330.0,
      "end_time": 79330.0,
      "text": "which is just about completed."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 79330.0,
      "end_time": 81330.0,
      "text": "It tells the story of Sputnik,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 81330.0,
      "end_time": 84330.0,
      "text": "and the story of what happened to America as a result."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 84330.0,
      "end_time": 86330.0,
      "text": "For days after the launch,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 86330.0,
      "end_time": 89330.0,
      "text": "Sputnik was a wonderful curiosity."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 89330.0,
      "end_time": 92330.0,
      "text": "A man-made moon visible by ordinary citizens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 93330.0,
      "end_time": 96330.0,
      "text": "it inspired awe and pride"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 96330.0,
      "end_time": 99330.0,
      "text": "that humans had finally launched an object into space."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 101330.0,
      "end_time": 104330.0,
      "text": "But just three days later, on a day they called Red Monday,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 104330.0,
      "end_time": 107330.0,
      "text": "the media and the politicians told us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 107330.0,
      "end_time": 109330.0,
      "text": "and we believed, that Sputnik was proof"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 109330.0,
      "end_time": 111330.0,
      "text": "that our enemy had beaten us"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 111330.0,
      "end_time": 114330.0,
      "text": "in science and technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 114330.0,
      "end_time": 117330.0,
      "text": "and that they could now attack us with hydrogen bombs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 117330.0,
      "end_time": 121330.0,
      "text": "using their Sputnik rocket as an IBM missile."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 121330.0,
      "end_time": 123330.0,
      "text": "All hell broke loose."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 123330.0,
      "end_time": 126330.0,
      "text": "Sputnik quickly became one of the three great shocks to hit America --"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 127330.0,
      "end_time": 130329.0,
      "text": "historians say the equal of Pearl Harbor or 9/11."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 131330.0,
      "end_time": 134330.0,
      "text": "It provoked the missile gap."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 134330.0,
      "end_time": 137330.0,
      "text": "It exploded an arms race."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 137330.0,
      "end_time": 140330.0,
      "text": "It began the space race."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 140330.0,
      "end_time": 143330.0,
      "text": "Within a year, Congress funded huge weapons increases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 143330.0,
      "end_time": 146330.0,
      "text": "and we went from 1,200 nuclear weapons"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 146330.0,
      "end_time": 148330.0,
      "text": "to 20,000."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 148330.0,
      "end_time": 151330.0,
      "text": "And the reactions to Sputnik went far beyond weapons increases."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 151330.0,
      "end_time": 154330.0,
      "text": "For example, some here will remember"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 154330.0,
      "end_time": 156330.0,
      "text": "this day, June 1958,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 156330.0,
      "end_time": 158330.0,
      "text": "the National Civil Defense Drill,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 158330.0,
      "end_time": 161330.0,
      "text": "where tens of millions of people in 78 cities went underground."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 162330.0,
      "end_time": 165330.0,
      "text": "Or the Gallup Poll that showed that seven in 10 Americans"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 165330.0,
      "end_time": 168330.0,
      "text": "believed that a nuclear war would happen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 168330.0,
      "end_time": 170330.0,
      "text": "and that at least 50 percent of our population"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 170330.0,
      "end_time": 172330.0,
      "text": "was going to be killed."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 172330.0,
      "end_time": 175330.0,
      "text": "But Sputnik provoked wonderful changes as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 176330.0,
      "end_time": 178330.0,
      "text": "For example, some in this room went to school on scholarship"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 178330.0,
      "end_time": 180330.0,
      "text": "because of Sputnik."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 180330.0,
      "end_time": 183330.0,
      "text": "Support for engineering, math and science --"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 183330.0,
      "end_time": 186330.0,
      "text": "education in general -- boomed."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 186330.0,
      "end_time": 188330.0,
      "text": "And Vint Cerf points out that Sputnik"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 188330.0,
      "end_time": 190330.0,
      "text": "led directly to ARPA, and the Internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 190330.0,
      "end_time": 193330.0,
      "text": "and, of course, NASA."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 193330.0,
      "end_time": 196330.0,
      "text": "My feature documentary shows how a free society"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 196330.0,
      "end_time": 199330.0,
      "text": "can be stampeded by those who know how to use media."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 199330.0,
      "end_time": 201330.0,
      "text": "But it also shows how we can turn"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 201330.0,
      "end_time": 204330.0,
      "text": "what appears at first to be a bad situation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 204330.0,
      "end_time": 207330.0,
      "text": "into something that was overall very good for America."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 208330.0,
      "end_time": 211330.0,
      "text": "\"Sputnik\" will soon be released."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 211330.0,
      "end_time": 213330.0,
      "text": "In closing, I would like to take a moment to thank"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 213330.0,
      "end_time": 215330.0,
      "text": "one of my investors:"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 215330.0,
      "end_time": 217330.0,
      "text": "longtime TEDster, Jay Walker."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 217330.0,
      "end_time": 219330.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;d like to thank you all."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 219330.0,
      "end_time": 223330.0,
      "text": "(Applause)."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 223330.0,
      "end_time": 224330.0,
      "text": "Thank you, Chris."
    }
  ]
}